The paper deals with scene text recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
